495m730w.name: 20 Advancements
495m730w.rules:
Get 20 advancements. You must show that you have 20 advancements via the advancements menu.

- If the last advancement is none of the below, time ends when you get the notification for that advancement.
- If the last advancement is "Minecraft", time ends either when you close the crafting GUI after crafting a crafting table or when you pick up the crafting table from the ground.
- If the last advancement is "Nether", time ends when you get the advancement "We Need to Go Deeper".
- If the last advancement is "End", time ends when you get the advancement "The End?".
- If the last advancement is "Adventure", time ends upon either getting the advancement "Monster Hunter", the killed entity tipping over in its dying animation, or the player respawning.
- If the last advancement is "Husbandry", time ends when the food disappears from your hotbar.
